/>\n間間大學都課金請出文機器刷排名<br />\n根本無人care教學質素 大把教書教到成pat屎嘅教授<br />\n讀大學只為執靚份cv搵好工 完全學唔到咩人生哲理社會時事邏輯思考<br />\n依家連八大校長都唔夠膽話會守護師生言論自由<br />\n恆大係雞校 但人地校長起碼肯講 唔會一邊話唔支持港獨 唔支持犯法言論 一邊話學生有言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:08:11.000Z","msg":"Lingu之前講到明冇錢追排名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉左個所謂博雅教育，放晒啲資源搞埋啲咩全宿制、最高9成exchange 率同 降低獎學金/助學金要求<br />\n但結果依然係香港人覺得因為低排名就當係野雞<br />\n有得揀邊個會真係揀lingu?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港社會好現實，排名係衡量一間大學地位嘅最主要因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLingu成間學校得2000人，無理科，上年都追到個QS Asia Top 100返黎<br />\n何況恒管有成5000個學位規模？<br />\n恒大講話唔追排名只係因為冇能力冇資源<br />\n有得追嘅話私校一定追得就追引人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c278c9278b19be29836ec5d5c44acfecdc973f6","tid":894572,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"叫人搵自己興趣，唔係為份工，其實先係教育"},{"pid":"03281c9f969d777791252a1c4000f99e4a49ba02","tid":894572,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c278c9278b19be29836ec5d5c44acfecdc973f6","tid":894572,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"叫人搵自己興趣，唔係為份工，其實先係教育"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊個唔識講"},{"pid":"8615ff76568887262751c99ebb36e507e290b23a","tid":894572,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03281c9f969d777791252a1c4000f99e4a49ba02","tid":894572,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c278c9278b19be29836ec5d5c44acfecdc973f6","tid":894572